articles.title: Man who rushed Ariana Grande at "Wicked: For Good" premiere faces charges in Singapore - CBS News
articles.description: Australian man Johnson Wen was charged with "being a public nuisance" after rushing Ariana Grande, according to court documents.
articles.content:
Singapore authorities charged an Australian man Friday for rushing film star Ariana Grande at the Asia premiere of "Wicked: For Good."
